              <h1 class=" fs-3xl m:fs-4xl l:fs-5xl fw-bold s:fw-heavy lh-tight mb-2 medium">
                Am I a Developer or Just a Prompt Engineer?
              </h1>
              
                  <div class="spec__tags flex flex-wrap">
                      <a class="crayons-tag   " style="
